text: Super Cyclonic Storm Kyarr was a powerful tropical cyclone that was the first super cyclonic storm since 2007. The storm moved across the Arabian Sea and affected Western India, Arabia, and Somalia. Nobody was killed from the storm, as it never tracked over land. ==References== Category:October 2019 events Category:November 2019 events Category:Tropical cyclones in Asia Category:2019 in weather
title: Cyclone Kyarr
